      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Task",
      "pos": [
        24455,
        24459
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Task metrics<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;/b&gt;</ph> are based on the status of tasks, such as Active, Pending, and Completed.",
      "pos": [
        24483,
